nodes.text: Fixer's landspeeder was a Landspeeder used by Laze "Fixer" Loneozner on Tatooine. It started life as a standard X-34 landspeeder with three engines, however Fixer mounted two additional salvaged X-34 engines to either side of the 'speeder's rear deck. This had the effect of increasing the vehicle's top speed, at a cost of fuel consumption. It could often be seen parked outside Tosche Station in Anchorhead.
